Primary Color: Deep Blue (#002F6C)
Represents trust, reliability, and professionalism.

Secondary Color: Vibrant Orange (#F77F00)
Adds energy and urgency, highlighting calls to action like "Add to Cart" or "Checkout."

Neutral Tones: Cool Gray (#F1F1F1, #6D6D6D)
Clean and modern, ideal for backgrounds and text.

Accent Color: Bright Green (#00C853)
Symbolizes growth and success, perfect for "Payment Successful" messages or highlights.